question 'Does the order in which the code for a button and the code for its event handler appear within the program matter?'
wrong 'Yes, the button, with its ID, must appear in the code AFTER the event handler.'
wrong 'No, JavaScript is flexible; the button and its event handler can appear in any order in the code.'
right 'Yes, the button, with its ID, must appear in the code BEFORE the event handler.'
